headline: Dow Jones Futures: Market Bounces On Trump Tariff Ruling; Iran News, Nvidia Earnings Key
summary: Dow Jones futures will open Sunday evening, along with S&P 500 futures and Nasdaq futures. Nvidia earnings loom with investors also watching out for U.S.-Iran developments. The stock market rose last week with the Nasdaq leading.
